lead_paragraph: Lazio remained fourth in Serie A with a 1-1 draw at Napoli after their striker Keita Balde Diao cancelled out Marek Hamsik's superb solo goal at the San Paolo stadium on Saturday.

headline.print_headline: Keita Earns Lazio Draw After Hamsik Strikes for Napoli
